headline: Align Technology to Announce Second Quarter 2025 Results on July 30, 2025
summary: TEMPE, Ariz., July 01, 2025--Align Technology, Inc. (Nasdaq: ALGN), a leading global medical device company that designs, manufactures, and sells the Invisalign® System of clear aligners, iTero™ intraoral scanners, and exocad™ CAD/CAM software for digital orthodontics and restorative dentistry, today announced that it will report second quarter 2025 financial results on Wednesday, July 30, 2025, after the close of market.
